{"tid":1540794,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"乜撚野「四大訴求」，依家係「五缺四」啊！","createTime":"2019-09-04T12:34:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T08:29:51.000Z","uid":246790,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"7f58232a97c3361bfcb654dc073e60fd7988094a","tid":1540794,"uid":246790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:34:05.000Z","msg":"想講<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」嘅口號有幾多人真係明白？<br />\n原意係五項訴求，只要任意缺少一項，都唔能接受！<br />\n依家只係應承會撤回<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">（未正式通過撤回動議，唔使咁開心住）</span></span>，只有一樣應承左，即係其餘四項都拒絕，顧名思義，依家係「五項缺四項」，唔能收貨！<br />\n<br />\n只要政府未應承五大訴求，呢場革命都未成功，所以要堅持「五大訴求，缺一不可」嘅初衷！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>五大訴求，缺一不可<br />\n光復香港，時代革命</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"839a7563f03d2bd31a7eaf67c92189c1d0ea51f4","tid":1540794,"uid":64268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:34:49.000Z","msg":"五大訴求，決一不可"},{"pid":"f46f925104b044e32bfa18a2c82f4f96b89faafa","tid":1540794,"uid":288912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:35:02.000Z","msg":"係回應左零個訴求呀懵撚<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1539958\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1539958</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"dbd410d21af4f86254c3d1dc987532ada69687a6","tid":1540794,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:36:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7f694836a3b397434e55a5f1bcd6e432a776be9e","tid":1540794,"uid":300521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:38:54.000Z","msg":"推！<br />\n撚唔撚識字呀，缺一不可呀DNLM"},{"pid":"32e8cc54ed6aea8693270cb3eb8f90893bb6d02c","tid":1540794,"uid":246790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:51:22.000Z","msg":"913 獅子山之路 齊慶中秋夜<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1531290\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1531290</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"31e788fdf72fb3d656d245af38a7efeafc122bc8",